Shipping, Returns & Customization

🚚

Delivery Policy

FREE delivery on orders above Rs. 799. Orders below Rs. 799 attract Rs. 99 delivery charges. Delhi NCR: 2-day express via Porter/Uber.

⚡

NCR Express

Delhi NCR customers get 2-day delivery! Porter or Uber pickup scheduled once your order is ready.

📦

Bulk Orders

Special pricing for bulk orders. Ideal for corporate gifting, weddings, return gifts, and festive hampers. Contact us on WhatsApp.

🎨

Customization

Customize fragrance, colour, jar, labels and branding, and gift packaging. Custom orders may need extra lead time.

🔄

Return Policy

Returns only for damaged products. Report within 24 hours with unboxing video. Mail: litpremiumcandles@gmail.com

✋

Handcrafted Note

All products are handcrafted with love. Slight variations may occur. Customized and bulk orders are non-returnable unless damaged.
